3. [Week 1] Fix pilot feedback → Phase 1 complete
4. [Week 2] Secure 1 pilot → Phase 2 begins
```

**Status: STRATEGICALLY SOUND.** Hackathon win = runway to Phase 2. No pilots by Month 3 = dead. Execute flawlessly. Pivot fast.

**First Milestone:** Deploy live demo by midnight. Pitch faculty tomorrow. Win hackathon first.